<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Nnodal</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-29 15:08:57</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>well to clear things up for you that don't know.<BR>
<BR>
The Crystaline Spear is dropped off Lady Vox in everfrost.<BR>
So get your buddies together do a raid and hope she drops it, its one of her uncommon drops.  Not the rareest but not everytime either.  This spear can only be used in the main hand.  It also doesn't sell for 200pp, dragon loot is normally not traded, handed down, or if traded tends to go for over 20kpp+ in items if its a good item such as this spear.<BR>
<BR>
As for the duel wield spear question.<BR>
<BR>
Several spears can be wielded in the off hand.  Two that come to mind are gloomwater harpoon 9/31 that drops in kedge<BR>
and the pre-patch jade Chocki'da Prod 11/30 +3 sta, +6 wis.<BR>
<BR>
Nnodal/Inudeeper<BR>
Cleric/Rogue</font></td></tr></table>
